      • preciseTurret

        public void preciseTurret(double power,
                          DriveDirections dir)
        Turns the turret at a given speed.
        Parameters:
        power - The power to turn the turret at. This should be positive, regardless of the direction to turn in.
        dir - The direction to turn in. This should be either DriveDirections.LEFT or DriveDirections.RIGHT. Anything else will stop the turret.
